OL,4,Ctaking them to protest
OL,6,FShe was then seen to throw a liquid
OL,7,Ffrom a bottle towards the police
OL,8,Fofficers after 'losing her temper'.
OL,10,FMitigating, Robert Moussalli said his
OL,11,Fclient, who wept throughout, was
OL,12,F'deeply sorry'.
OL,14,F"She was taking her child to her
OL,15,Fgrandmother's when she saw her auntie
OL,16,Fstanding with some people near the
OL,17,Fhotel and went to talk to her," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
