OL,3,CMother put 'own child at risk' after
OL,4,Ctaking them to protest
OL,6,F"Then people started shouting and she
OL,7,Fmoved to the front of the group and
OL,8,Fher auntie went to the back with her
OL,9,Fchild. She wasn't planning to do
OL,10,Fanything."
OL,12,FHe said Smith had thrown water, but it
OL,13,Fhad not made contact with the officers.
OL,15,FHe added that she "lost her temper"
OL,16,Fwhen someone from behind the police
OL,17,F"shouted at her."
OL,19,F"I accept she brought it entirely on
OL,20,Fherself," Mr Moussalli added.
