OL,6,FGranting her bail with stringent
OL,7,Fconditions, District Judge Joanne
OL,8,FHirst said: "I am prepared to give you
OL,9,Fone opportunity. You put your own
OL,10,Fchild at risk."
OL,12,FMichelle Jibson, 45, and Tracy
OL,13,FPearson, 53, both of Kingsbridge Road,
OL,14,FManchester, also pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Fviolent disorder.
OL,17,FThey were both described as
OL,18,F'agitators' after being alleged to
OL,19,Fhave attended outside the hotel on
OL,20,FOldham Road on July 31.
