OL,6,FJibson was said to be wearing a yellow
OL,7,Fshirt with an England flag wrapped
OL,8,Faround her waist.
OL,10,F"She is seen to strike out at a police
OL,11,Fofficer during a verbal provocation,"
OL,12,Fprosecutor Tess Kenyon said.
OL,14,F"She doesn't remove herself despite
OL,15,Frequests by the police to move on."
OL,17,FJibson was said to have 'genuine
OL,18,Fremorse'.
