OL,6,FPearson was said to have attended
OL,7,Foutside the hotel, and was also
OL,8,Fwearing an England flag wrapped around
OL,9,Fher waist.
OL,11,FShe was said to be verbally
OL,12,Fprovocative to the police, shouting:
OL,13,F"F*** off - I can't believe you lot
OL,14,Fsticking up for that s**t in there."
OL,16,FMs Shaw, representing both, said of
OL,17,FPearson: "She is very sorry. She
OL,18,Fwished she didn't attend at the time."
