OL,6,FBoth women were remanded into custody,
OL,7,Fwhile Smith was granted bail with
OL,8,Fconditions. All three will be
OL,9,Fsentenced on 19 August.
OL,11,FThe hearings follow a wave of violent
OL,12,Fdisorder in the days after the fatal
OL,13,Fstabbing of three young girls in
OL,14,FSouthport which triggered riots across
OL,15,Fthe country.
OL,17,FViolent scenes were seen across the
OL,18,FNorth West in places including
OL,19,FSouthport, Liverpool, Blackpool,
OL,20,FBolton, and Manchester city centre.
