OL,6,FOne youngster, in Manchester, was said
OL,7,Fto have been "more involved in the
OL,8,Fviolence and disorder than any other
OL,9,Fdefendant I've seen," by a judge as he
OL,10,Fappeared in court.
OL,12,FIn Southport, another 12-year-old was
OL,13,Fcaught on CCTV throwing an object at a
OL,14,Fline of police before riding off on a
OL,15,Fbike, Liverpool Youth Court heard.
